<body>
    <h1>T4 - Requirement Analysis Document</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <h1 local-id=3D"2db33fe2e054" id=3D"T4-RequirementAnalysisDocument-=
1.Introduction">1. Introduction</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"15af557011cc" id=3D"T4-RequirementAnalysisDocument-1.1Purpo=
se">1.1 Purpose</h2>
<p local-id=3D"7e3b14696758">This document defines the requirements for dep=
loying three frontend applications (Air-Quality, Bookshop, and Notesapp) on=
 Amazon Web Services (AWS) using three different services: Amazon EC2, Amaz=
on ECS (Fargate), and Amazon S3.</p>
<p local-id=3D"cb09b1a34a3e">The intended audience of this document include=
s:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"c7fd5409-8933-4948-84c5-e23353dbad97">
<li local-id=3D"ed061d8e-e35d-4468-9dfd-697f15c9558e">
<p local-id=3D"3099c0d857f9">CTO</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9c7b5d08-52ab-4acc-a3bc-cc4e80f2b040">
<p local-id=3D"a78891a325b0">Solution Architect</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4efd07df-dd36-47f4-b744-652480d9034d">
<p local-id=3D"beb88d4618d5">DevOps Engineers</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"74b7575a-1090-4c34-ad6d-5a84709934f3">
<p local-id=3D"09565dda6a24">Developers</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e6a4f94a-9954-4cec-8df3-6b025be274b0">
<p local-id=3D"1a566fbea243">Technical Review Team</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"b8d9d3cc8908">This document serves as a reference for unders=
tanding the deployment requirements, system behavior, constraints, and eval=
uation criteria for selecting a standard frontend deployment service.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"7a5c2a53-a3eb-453e-93fd-9e9860e805a0">
<h2 local-id=3D"32069220635c" id=3D"T4-RequirementAnalysisDocument-1.2Scope=
">1.2 Scope</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"70e699ae182b" id=3D"T4-RequirementAnalysisDocument-InScope"=
>In Scope</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"0567a41f-c383-4d6b-868f-398ae8b1ca06">
<li local-id=3D"ce7598cb-03e2-4b80-a578-878c9783e7fa">
<p local-id=3D"997861a78a70">Deployment of the following frontend applicati=
ons:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"7cd54761-a221-41f3-a33d-c6ecc0de53a4">
<li local-id=3D"02f0b02b-892d-40d4-bd8d-eee51ecf27b2">
<p local-id=3D"bd4ed971c4d2">Air-Quality</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9cb58a64-e7c2-4db7-bddd-35bf871665fc">
<p local-id=3D"5b28b6308537">Bookshop</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"50584a87-405a-4689-9846-b8ec8c94ae98">
<p local-id=3D"11e18d8ecaed">Notesapp</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"50463a7a-c4f2-4708-a55d-abbf27456fb5">
<p local-id=3D"152b391c55ac">Deployment on:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"dd8d8dfa-2efd-42c7-9e2b-6b19e164ad50">
<li local-id=3D"96f55aff-3020-44a7-95e4-f95faf723245">
<p local-id=3D"3c4777d8216c">Amazon EC2 (with Nginx)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a9dcfaa3-8e6c-4bd5-899f-1575a0119a52">
<p local-id=3D"55bd103687f7">Amazon ECS (Fargate with ECR and ALB)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a96bae01-1670-41fb-a74f-1cfde700625d">
<p local-id=3D"47fdbd79cd26">Amazon S3 (Static Website Hosting)</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"3b0da107-5e42-4064-9510-c83be9b7efed">
<p local-id=3D"cd85d47ec5e7">Dockerization of applications for ECS</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1f1a580d-0684-484c-b855-f323083d1d89">
<p local-id=3D"616c05e6b79f">Pushing container images to Amazon ECR</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"ab5273aa-64eb-45ac-99da-878b13b1c2e9">
<p local-id=3D"6b9f8e0a6118">Configuring networking and public accessibilit=
y</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"151aa5c2-fa15-4be9-bbaa-d83e66f4a519">
<p local-id=3D"aacdd7584906">Comparing the three services</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5db369a0-8189-42f5-887f-68be212e7a68">
<p local-id=3D"2738e46ef50c">Providing a recommendation for standard fronte=
nd deployment</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"cd1aa09e178d" id=3D"T4-RequirementAnalysisDocument-OutofSco=
pe">Out of Scope</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"91dabecc-d1b4-4348-a3d8-8f348c08fd05">
<li local-id=3D"c2422b2f-ac41-490d-b5ba-a3c65f73e070">
<p local-id=3D"0f36d7383b86">Backend service development</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f7ef2227-88fb-420b-88ca-5fcab8420202">
<p local-id=3D"03bf94a6b24b">Database configuration</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7a88cc25-03f6-4742-b62b-5ed5a6240860">
<p local-id=3D"c2818fc72285">CI/CD pipeline automation</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b7b7c769-0fd6-4a7b-8b54-1c3a3c9700a1">
<p local-id=3D"4b1af1e9c4c6">Domain name registration and Route53 configura=
tion</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e753d7a4-47bc-4796-922a-bf5996a22296">
<p local-id=3D"3b3e02d99326">Production-grade monitoring and logging setup<=
/p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"35b36455-4089-4dfb-9fa3-cb66a1c8e8c9">
