<hr local-id=3D"5ecf6016-344c-41a7-987b-7e2b6504510f">
<h2 local-id=3D"2a63bc19062d" id=3D"T4-RequirementAnalysisDocument-1.5Overv=
iew">1.5 Overview</h2>
<p local-id=3D"6a9628d1e1c8">This document is structured as follows:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"b6d851a8-6e41-4aff-932d-328952c94017">
<li local-id=3D"323e8df2-509f-4188-bc3a-f2a0056cb0ab">
<p local-id=3D"d1a3db70d01c">Section 2 describes the project overview and o=
bjectives.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d7b2d192-50a1-4afc-a564-2fa4fb432e5b">
<p local-id=3D"dffa6e5981e0">Section 3 defines functional requirements and =
use cases.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8f7cef3c-b5d5-4ba5-9788-83175e6cacdb">
<p local-id=3D"7994a137a516">Section 4 outlines non-functional requirements=
.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bdf97700-85e6-4fbe-93ee-6b5bc4aa8d47">
<p local-id=3D"bd5370803720">Section 5 lists assumptions and dependencies.<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2b75d9ba-4326-4bc5-bc91-bc12c252e84d">
<p local-id=3D"285a4223277f">Section 6 covers risk analysis.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0732183d-8928-4840-8bed-f38b43434422">
<p local-id=3D"66cc73a8b929">Section 7 provides glossary definitions.</p></=
li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"7a7c075a-4de8-437e-88bf-fe5891676f80">
<h1 local-id=3D"312e656f8ded" id=3D"T4-RequirementAnalysisDocument-2.Projec=
tOverview">2. Project Overview</h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"39f87a33c372" id=3D"T4-RequirementAnalysisDocument-2.1Proje=
ctObjectives">2.1 Project Objectives</h2>
<p local-id=3D"5213a639f3e0">The primary objectives of this project are:</p=
>
<ul local-id=3D"e21315d7-befe-414a-98ab-5642680ed0c0">
<li local-id=3D"de975fda-0a6a-4731-9814-3d7181774adf">
<p local-id=3D"06a7c234127e">Deploy three frontend applications using three=
 different AWS services.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bab8ab74-a856-48b2-977d-8942e773a50d">
<p local-id=3D"fea48e97581f">Evaluate operational, scalability, cost, and m=
anagement aspects.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9c21ec06-4dc7-4361-bf4e-078dc3a902e8">
<p local-id=3D"846bbc7c2b36">Identify the most suitable AWS service for sta=
ndardized frontend deployment.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fef8df7a-0aec-485f-8203-0d78709a8fb4">
<p local-id=3D"81f88a31af2c">Ensure applications are publicly accessible an=
d operational.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"37e771ed-a5c8-4ba3-9cf9-1e15126c42e0">
<h2 local-id=3D"0a2fe409a594" id=3D"T4-RequirementAnalysisDocument-2.2Busin=
essGoals">2.2 Business Goals</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"f95d6789-b5e3-431f-a155-35c34fa632f7">
<li local-id=3D"01f5dcba-8125-4604-8c40-92107e896b1f">
<p local-id=3D"aebd8c03c33c">Standardize frontend deployment architecture.<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d993be46-b924-4767-a369-a98dfdbc88a5">
<p local-id=3D"1575fa2b9a84">Reduce operational complexity.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"640148e7-3cbb-46d5-a919-1b729a0d8481">
<p local-id=3D"3bd618b49adf">Optimize infrastructure cost.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3d03125a-1fb0-415e-b16f-9a478d727eec">
<p local-id=3D"e04bd58079da">Improve scalability and maintainability.</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"8a0c097b-0b05-4a0a-806a-32c7523d04b5">
<p local-id=3D"31cd5e80a7c0">Enable easier replication of deployment across=
 projects.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"8800353d-29a6-407c-9cc3-167505ab28d7">
<h2 local-id=3D"254b89eb436d" id=3D"T4-RequirementAnalysisDocument-2.3Backg=
round">2.3 Background</h2>
<p local-id=3D"1bd5dcba20c1">The organization requires a standardized appro=
ach for deploying frontend applications in the cloud. Currently, multiple A=
WS services can host static frontend applications, including EC2, ECS, and =
S3.</p>
<p local-id=3D"651f170ac93b">This project evaluates these options by practi=
cally deploying three frontend applications across all three services and a=
nalyzing their suitability.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"e2e0ae0f-7006-4f66-9a88-a84d3457d52b">
<h2 local-id=3D"5f72adcb5d95" id=3D"T4-RequirementAnalysisDocument-2.4Const=
raints">2.4 Constraints</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"6b0d5301-873c-430b-befb-9db03550f1d9">
<li local-id=3D"21fcf55e-91cd-467a-a159-2a96176c6201">
<p local-id=3D"2c39e658c009">Time constraint: 5 hours for implementation an=
d documentation.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9a6572be-8de6-493b-bac5-1ca441e4eb1a">
<p local-id=3D"b7888afa9639">Budget constraint: AWS Free Tier usage.</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"ddfcde02-168c-4ccb-8a96-d6014f3a6d15">
<p local-id=3D"82637bc7afca">Technology constraint: Frontend-only applicati=
ons (HTML, CSS, JS).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"649c9e44-5075-4ede-94be-74d4d5d7383d">
<p local-id=3D"0569444ea492">No use of advanced DevOps automation (manual d=
eployment).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a5152430-32b9-4804-9894-d8d5f84a3077">
<p local-id=3D"59a7772160f2">No custom domain configuration.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"02c82e2b-259e-4435-a891-a5c7c2354532">
<h1 local-id=3D"280871688967" id=3D"T4-RequirementAnalysisDocument-3.Functi=
onalRequirements">3. Functional Requirements</h1>
<hr local-id=3D"c055cb98-05ce-4f91-a438-93bd360c62dc">
<h2 local-id=3D"d5e6dc46ade5" id=3D"T4-RequirementAnalysisDocument-3.1UseCa=
seDiagram">3.1 Use Case Diagram</h2><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file=
-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=
=3D"confluence-embedded-image image-center" alt=3D"image-20260309-182743.pn=
g" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"d05a2f802ae2eca86eeaa14e652b2886d2=
f641c0ccaa3fc952dbcbbcae3ea4f6" data-image-src=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.=
net/wiki/download/attachments/1787461695/image-20260309-182743.png?version=
=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D1773080866370&amp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2=
" data-height=3D"832" data-width=3D"1101" data-unresolved-comment-count=3D"=
0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"1844019300" data-linked-resource-version=3D"1=
" data-linked-resource-type=3D"attachment" data-linked-resource-default-ali=
as=3D"image-20260309-182743.png" data-base-url=3D"https://iamops.atlassian.=
net/wiki" data-linked-resource-content-type=3D"image/png" data-linked-resou=
rce-container-id=3D"1787461695" data-linked-resource-container-version=3D"3=
" data-media-id=3D"2eb73e6f-068a-4883-97eb-d43195980dd0" data-media-type=3D=
"file" height=3D"353"></span>
<h3 local-id=3D"e4fcebc8daee" id=3D"T4-RequirementAnalysisDocument-Actors:"=
>Actors:</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"ca8d3dc4-65e4-4ee9-987f-b89035be66cc">
<li local-id=3D"6ecf482a-6627-4793-bf7c-6a2c746a8294">
<p local-id=3D"9945778cc3e1">DevOps Engineer</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bfb332c7-4be6-405d-a436-ef7c7283191f">
<p local-id=3D"17355817d8a8">End User</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"011c3c8effc5" id=3D"T4-RequirementAnalysisDocument-CoreUseC=
ases:">Core Use Cases:</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"fbb5083c-dd85-4476-9014-45ed62ca1275">
<li local-id=3D"afc7d7ee-3e72-4bd4-9882-a707427ffece">
<p local-id=3D"c0db6968a111">Deploy frontend application on EC2</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7982b3f6-8dd4-4e10-a6eb-661828d2fd89">
<p local-id=3D"a5956cc6c0cb">Deploy frontend application on ECS</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"999eb8ac-1816-4280-874c-e48c28c121a2">
<p local-id=3D"5ca7c73ac123">Deploy frontend application on S3</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8e5c1438-2d0d-4638-8971-4ba81d6f0fb3">
<p local-id=3D"590083a388dd">Access application via public endpoint</p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"f19acd12-3da2-40af-a88d-c779c8efdeaa">
<p local-id=3D"849b27c1ba14">Compare deployment services</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"68e7b030-ec1e-48c1-a3d0-8e8af187a9e5">
<h2 local-id=3D"c92c209f6435" id=3D"T4-RequirementAnalysisDocument-3.2UseCa=
ses">3.2 Use Cases</h2>
<hr local-id=3D"c58ff18c-5627-4f7e-bd9c-811b014bcb5d">
<h2 local-id=3D"bb529cfa8572" id=3D"T4-RequirementAnalysisDocument-3.2.1Use=
Case1:DeployApplicationonEC2">3.2.1 Use Case 1: Deploy Application on EC2</=
h2>
<p local-id=3D"244b24ae14ac"><strong>Description:</strong><br>
Deploy a frontend application on an EC2 instance using Nginx.</p>
<p local-id=3D"098d1eee7ddb"><strong>Actors:</strong><br>
DevOps Engineer</p>
<p local-id=3D"846cc8276b05"><strong>Preconditions:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"5b4052dd-3770-45dc-bd70-ae5d074a7efa">
<li local-id=3D"e29406a9-e5ef-455b-8d48-a57dd4d71fa8">
<p local-id=3D"56ee040b42ff">AWS account available</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f06acfb8-f0ea-43d0-b8ee-a67bc1c1a145">
<p local-id=3D"88f4eecbee1a">EC2 instance running</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ce5eacf8-4b1f-4ebd-979d-03feda221776">
<p local-id=3D"60074b229a18">Security group allows HTTP (port 80)</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"68b28667e909"><strong>Postconditions:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"ade8bd38-af0c-40e7-8529-c7f88708801c">
<li local-id=3D"771ba919-68e2-4c33-9819-c07e8ea981c9">
<p local-id=3D"ff8d7f781d24">Application accessible via EC2 public IP</p></=
li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"f56ca83f1c9c"><strong>Flow of Events:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"ca3d8254-a8b1-42e0-904a-b63141c63224">
<li local-id=3D"7b29f922-7114-4a67-a6ff-6fc6bb472e20">
<p local-id=3D"329fa6161a96">Launch EC2 instance.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1f3169d8-36be-48a2-9f11-6249430ccf54">
<p local-id=3D"1f8f4951047b">Install Nginx.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7d78a962-705a-4915-8658-0f395775a862">
<p local-id=3D"325926c2fb60">Remove default web files.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"49fed899-b423-472d-8542-69006d9ecad2">
<p local-id=3D"f613312e5df0">Upload frontend project files.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bbfbe1a3-2709-408d-a009-f1f7b1797d81">
<p local-id=3D"a78f18821d67">Restart Nginx.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4a0a2ee9-85cd-46a6-8822-0c7b27acb431">
<p local-id=3D"dcc07e05d24a">Verify application via public IP.</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"e51ab8eefa3a"><strong>Alternative Flows:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"9f710790-1a97-438f-92c8-e06716d2640f">
<li local-id=3D"8bbf53c5-6f9f-4681-93f6-c8f307e16557">
<p local-id=3D"16b232ea566f">Security group misconfiguration blocks access.=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9a0b10c6-d4ce-43fd-83d5-7e9e60b592eb">
<p local-id=3D"8d9e94b35c11">Nginx service fails to start.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"39e42225-bcf9-41d0-b190-f02210dc60cd">
<h2 local-id=3D"7ff20d76adae" id=3D"T4-RequirementAnalysisDocument-3.2.2Use=
Case2:DeployApplicationonECS(Fargate)">3.2.2 Use Case 2: Deploy Application=
 on ECS (Fargate)</h2>
<p local-id=3D"f5173e7e7a82"><strong>Description:</strong><br>
Deploy containerized frontend application using ECS Fargate.</p>
<p local-id=3D"745d4d78408d"><strong>Actors:</strong><br>
DevOps Engineer</p>
<p local-id=3D"832a6b94d944"><strong>Preconditions:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"31bee042-e53b-4451-b488-5eb4e907fe41">
<li local-id=3D"5ac202f3-6d27-40d6-881c-5e45fc58c7ac">
<p local-id=3D"8c74949ba1d9">Docker installed locally</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ba380a74-42ef-41a3-89b5-9249fb266da7">
<p local-id=3D"da6c35e79148">AWS CLI configured</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"53d23d7c-17ef-483a-893e-bdc143eb5c9d">
<p local-id=3D"f032f532a433">ECR repository created</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"7f95720c00db"><strong>Postconditions:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"7b17334d-b051-424d-9856-50c34d19b675">
<li local-id=3D"7b4f1b24-4f91-4733-91b0-1bd2591c08a3">
<p local-id=3D"c407d762d503">Application accessible via ALB DNS</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"5aef2fbc28f1"><strong>Flow of Events:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"24901b12-54a1-464a-b143-945a0b969102">
<li local-id=3D"0ea33558-eaf2-4573-aa3c-ffe238250540">
<p local-id=3D"02308bf3f9d4">Create Dockerfile.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"da78d66d-f61c-4bc3-b20c-fb4c765c4813">
<p local-id=3D"cdf04b196cec">Build Docker image.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2eb92521-9ac3-4402-a434-3d2b88020bd3">
<p local-id=3D"685081bd6a36">Push image to ECR.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c4d1c112-4a4a-45de-83b3-cbd9a0b14e39">
<p local-id=3D"e6d3e14acf9d">Create ECS task definition.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ecdcc112-b63c-4239-9de1-dda3b862a74b">
<p local-id=3D"d040f8f6aa60">Create ECS service with ALB.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"74486b07-485b-4b9f-82ab-96339eec7171">
<p local-id=3D"35b9a0028b67">Verify application via Load Balancer URL.</p><=
/li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"e1b2b6f05d5c"><strong>Alternative Flows:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"ac1bcb59-a662-4f89-8623-7b8758e5b6c5">
<li local-id=3D"de292071-7c46-4231-8cff-f400c9554431">
<p local-id=3D"b6f11abb1f6d">Image push fails.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4bdc9f8e-8d29-4fc1-87e6-4a977dd45f70">
<p local-id=3D"85f1ce7eb8fb">Task fails health check.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"790b58ee-5e24-49fb-8d8d-85a656e71b37">
<p local-id=3D"31403ea17648">Load balancer misconfiguration.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"c8559609-f83a-4ce5-b709-eca2889e447d">
<h2 local-id=3D"32e32f267542" id=3D"T4-RequirementAnalysisDocument-3.2.3Use=
Case3:DeployApplicationonS3">3.2.3 Use Case 3: Deploy Application on S3</h2=
>
<p local-id=3D"db736ffaaaac"><strong>Description:</strong><br>
Deploy static frontend application using S3 static hosting.</p>
<p local-id=3D"c60bd9848346"><strong>Actors:</strong><br>
DevOps Engineer</p>
<p local-id=3D"74b816df5992"><strong>Preconditions:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"3d6387ba-caa4-4c04-9619-17790dd290ff">
<li local-id=3D"e1850696-8137-48ed-8300-afd1fc5b1a2a">
<p local-id=3D"5086614cc842">S3 bucket created</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6c1adcd1-01e1-480c-ab21-b065c26b1c1e">
<p local-id=3D"9f28a78296a9">Public access configured</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"d08b22337b10"><strong>Postconditions:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"2fb94b83-247d-4516-94cc-e539c841516f">
<li local-id=3D"76094a40-42dd-4a08-a0a2-cceaa231996e">
<p local-id=3D"dd9cedcb3f6c">Application accessible via S3 website endpoint=
</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"0df02558390c"><strong>Flow of Events:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"80a2fd08-f458-4c6a-8127-2302e7e4e7e7">
<li local-id=3D"8b4907ed-9db6-4963-b257-5f88651b2a0f">
<p local-id=3D"20aea1c4f857">Create S3 bucket.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"64d44b4d-abe2-4b47-9e03-66b1eba8a327">
<p local-id=3D"2b4d5c312d6c">Enable static website hosting.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5ba884a3-e5b2-4184-867e-e67dd84e173c">
<p local-id=3D"7af1d4b48c09">Upload project files.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"44e65898-c34f-410a-83ae-6f853713d0cc">
<p local-id=3D"64a740309c35">Configure bucket policy.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9d5f9a76-6082-4535-987b-ae4a27ba1233">
<p local-id=3D"73751b602dc4">Verify website URL.</p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"fb8bc61b4dcd"><strong>Alternative Flows:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"f9ccc7f6-aaa8-45c2-b78a-da9bb9c526f6">
<li local-id=3D"e64a4f63-2617-4527-8061-f332754811c2">
<p local-id=3D"fec6cb32d445">403 Access Denied error.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e5e2b90a-1e9f-45f1-a30c-6034081976bc">
<p local-id=3D"8bbc3fcb6bab">Incorrect index document configuration.</p></l=
i>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"1e9bd109-3613-4b5b-b02c-84e03c5740a4">
<h2 local-id=3D"e4418fad285b" id=3D"T4-RequirementAnalysisDocument-3.2.4Use=
Case4:EndUserAccessApplication">3.2.4 Use Case 4: End User Access Applicati=
on</h2>
<p local-id=3D"81f4b5375da7"><strong>Description:</strong><br>
User accesses deployed application.</p>
<p local-id=3D"287f771339b1"><strong>Actors:</strong><br>
End User</p>
<p local-id=3D"07c33d55f640"><strong>Preconditions:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"9095eea2-0776-48ec-8039-d0e0af26c243">
<li local-id=3D"2b7635a6-fb8b-4209-bdea-738d9120a57f">
<p local-id=3D"02b35939eeb6">Application successfully deployed</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"602eb29bfa36"><strong>Postconditions:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"10807f7b-85f5-4234-8777-b3cd76425933">
<li local-id=3D"550efb26-ca1b-4cdd-9e2b-ac4169fd5121">
<p local-id=3D"13f61d5b014c">Application interface loads successfully</p></=
li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"29980eab247b"><strong>Flow of Events:</strong></p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"65b31c50-cedc-4b5d-b48a-5dcd7a6e7638">
<li local-id=3D"1ccdd5e4-35ce-4ebf-a748-2a8d09b8462c">
<p local-id=3D"0cd85776ddf4">User opens public URL.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c290246d-67e2-48a6-893e-1463213a3aa5">
<p local-id=3D"6cc593300fa0">Application loads.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7fa29efa-8bd9-4047-8f5e-4b68377884d2">
<p local-id=3D"203bb41f2780">User interacts with frontend.</p></li>
</ol>
<hr local-id=3D"43231d60-9fa5-4331-a477-a1eace1edb4f">
<h1 local-id=3D"1c50416f7b25" id=3D"T4-RequirementAnalysisDocument-4.Non-Fu=
nctionalRequirements">4. Non-Functional Requirements</h1>
<hr local-id=3D"cad25e47-bc8b-469d-b422-c22f685af787">
<h2 local-id=3D"e9b84af5769f" id=3D"T4-RequirementAnalysisDocument-4.1Perfo=
rmanceRequirements">4.1 Performance Requirements</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"33061cd1-897c-4bc3-9888-aaade99e86b8">
<li local-id=3D"ee719444-4126-47d3-8cdc-f49b47b86fad">
<p local-id=3D"2e9fda8f0c4a">Application response time should be under 2 se=
conds.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"73704f99-0891-4d2b-8850-7772b2fa2858">
<p local-id=3D"13d59df0e7ed">ECS service must pass health checks.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6a4262fe-4b50-407c-8ed2-42cc8206ef18">
<p local-id=3D"7ce3bf53c394">EC2 instance must handle standard HTTP traffic=
.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b2c646ec-9d3c-4940-8ed0-f1bd63fe35c1">
<p local-id=3D"1662441f22ce">S3 hosting must deliver static files efficient=
ly.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"b0a58ae5-f647-489c-997e-abae9b485efc">
<h2 local-id=3D"73cd0d05b3d6" id=3D"T4-RequirementAnalysisDocument-4.2Secur=
ityRequirements">4.2 Security Requirements</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"e6062d6a-6610-43ce-a638-61a3d1611fa5">
<li local-id=3D"d3a2c8d2-bfdd-4d6c-91f3-357d80ff3d5f">
<p local-id=3D"c13e152dc614">EC2 security group allows only required ports.=
</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ff8dbe67-74fa-49b4-9e57-d45d345fe996">
<p local-id=3D"cd877b5688ae">IAM roles and policies follow least privilege =
principle.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8a75db3d-28b5-4123-bc14-a13381babd6c">
<p local-id=3D"d3de7dbf2f2e">ECR authentication required for image push.</p=
></li>
<li local-id=3D"081594e6-0808-48dd-802f-478cd09f493d">
<p local-id=3D"f48850f6ae68">S3 bucket policy configured explicitly for pub=
lic read.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"1645578c-e5b9-44c9-a816-6a953879db8c">
<h2 local-id=3D"71833d5ade41" id=3D"T4-RequirementAnalysisDocument-4.3Usabi=
lityRequirements">4.3 Usability Requirements</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"832d9dd1-40bf-41ac-a8dc-a5db14605469">
<li local-id=3D"1507239e-2eaa-418b-be6b-db8fc16359f6">
<p local-id=3D"4291c1e20ccf">Applications must be accessible via browser.</=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9598c878-118b-45c2-8d53-8cc94c879a9d">
<p local-id=3D"00d09fe9397f">Public endpoints must load without authenticat=
ion.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"998781b7-c1ab-41ba-bfb5-6e350abeeaa3">
<p local-id=3D"a6f63348e19b">No additional client configuration required.</=
p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"c204589c-f089-47f4-866c-caf7a04312e9">
<h2 local-id=3D"99ce6111bdc7" id=3D"T4-RequirementAnalysisDocument-4.4Relia=
bilityRequirements">4.4 Reliability Requirements</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"1ab497b6-63aa-40a8-a16a-7fcbe779cb51">
<li local-id=3D"78500021-131d-4a2e-82ec-ea8457dd5299">
<p local-id=3D"d4a9dee322b2">ECS service maintains task availability.</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"13c71e2e-0bf5-4cbf-a72d-241bf0599516">
<p local-id=3D"88194c5149ca">EC2 instance must remain in running state.</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"1ea6467e-e738-4957-9283-1552a99ba4f1">
<p local-id=3D"61a5b4c32f9d">S3 hosting must be continuously available.</p>=
</li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"98fa5b40-a600-4546-9146-382f4fad9c53">
<h2 local-id=3D"c79deaff71cf" id=3D"T4-RequirementAnalysisDocument-4.5Compl=
ianceRequirements">4.5 Compliance Requirements</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"67deeb8d-b568-4a8a-846c-2858ae274048">
<li local-id=3D"4d891995-1bd0-42a7-804d-37569ccaa3b6">
<p local-id=3D"1e893b17ec66">Follow AWS best practices.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c0e168ee-b42d-41f7-9e29-6c7a3975567c">
<p local-id=3D"7582fee72a96">No sensitive data stored in frontend.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"070b2a32-2899-4d20-b04b-e5f7254c49e5">
<p local-id=3D"99674a8388b1">IAM usage aligned with AWS security guidelines=
.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"233d95ce-7862-440d-9fc5-b1ed9fa48dab">
<h1 local-id=3D"cb0726e83b72" id=3D"T4-RequirementAnalysisDocument-5.Assump=
tionsandDependencies">5. Assumptions and Dependencies</h1>
<hr local-id=3D"d30b1ade-df53-4d97-8a38-57b508c2f908">
<h2 local-id=3D"aa1e88aee3ca" id=3D"T4-RequirementAnalysisDocument-5.1Assum=
ptions">5.1 Assumptions</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"9ec942fa-bf50-48b9-bab2-3e71be984658">
<li local-id=3D"86e59ae0-6d8c-4f86-b3a2-88fed769fa88">
<p local-id=3D"2683d7ac2a27">Applications are purely frontend (HTML, CSS, J=
S).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"adddcb38-a283-4887-a2b4-6784dcfb1a32">
<p local-id=3D"dec233d85c3c">No backend integration required.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e39b5284-3d32-4a9d-be56-124650f7a603">
<p local-id=3D"48b5ad443326">AWS Free Tier sufficient for deployment.</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"69450394-46b7-426f-a7ec-b9a5c9714c3c">
<p local-id=3D"50d93a88498f">Public internet access is allowed.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"c03b2088-28a4-4c5f-84af-4931c6ced3a6">
<h2 local-id=3D"e3fb77e539b4" id=3D"T4-RequirementAnalysisDocument-5.2Depen=
dencies">5.2 Dependencies</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"ec23d6c0-3fc8-4a5b-a0f4-301ab17d298b">
<li local-id=3D"914f2e28-b0d7-46d8-9250-abf16510c4ad">
<p local-id=3D"529e54fdffa1">AWS account availability.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e9483dbe-79b4-4410-995a-df3779513680">
<p local-id=3D"b9acf7f3cc03">Docker installation.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0d723f4d-62c5-406f-af13-9b43c97ad8f4">
<p local-id=3D"ef7e4450d9ec">Stable internet connection.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"19a10e73-ae5c-4797-99eb-0d9d26df29cc">
<p local-id=3D"d9871f02eebd">Proper IAM configuration.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"6a232dc8-ee2c-47c9-abe5-1c84fda5fe6e">
<h1 local-id=3D"8f7b2a5d334b" id=3D"T4-RequirementAnalysisDocument-6.RiskAn=
alysis">6. Risk Analysis</h1>
<hr local-id=3D"5011e90d-af80-45e1-9d67-b3fdd1014cc3">
<h2 local-id=3D"ab74f8d5b774" id=3D"T4-RequirementAnalysisDocument-6.1RiskI=
dentification">6.1 Risk Identification</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"43354464-7518-4dde-af81-c21d0d6c4716">
<li local-id=3D"1187042b-5b1d-4de8-9cb7-e8d3023dba88">
<p local-id=3D"778ec3b409b6">Misconfigured IAM policies.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a9631972-cfb2-4010-9a6b-56a5688d19b6">
<p local-id=3D"77034550e44c">Security group misconfiguration.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f3f99237-33d4-4c4a-8485-3e4df409e54c">
<p local-id=3D"b847250eaf3b">Incorrect S3 bucket policy.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d49ff7ff-efbb-4b91-8fa6-564fe53956b7">
<p local-id=3D"eb0b43948b70">ECS task health check failure.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a5947d72-9a08-47a1-8559-f9ca70b75f4c">
<p local-id=3D"7bd2cd5dfa29">Unexpected AWS cost usage.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"21afad9c-2c7f-4622-9994-cce807e91f50">
<h2 local-id=3D"7464c5cf3d9d" id=3D"T4-RequirementAnalysisDocument-6.2RiskM=
itigation">6.2 Risk Mitigation</h2>
<ul local-id=3D"13cdd2f6-db9a-4dd9-97a4-bd48d4754c5f">
<li local-id=3D"9e7b07b6-31e9-4e29-ad53-6f3e16816b1c">
<p local-id=3D"baf72cbb391d">Validate IAM roles before deployment.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a799367f-1feb-41f3-a7b1-4a92b2ab7320">
<p local-id=3D"445d1b642792">Test access after each deployment step.</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"368df5e0-8e88-411a-ba6b-7a55bcabaf2b">
<p local-id=3D"6742ab27f4b2">Use AWS Free Tier resources.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3697e026-1f9a-4c47-9fc2-b9bc8395198c">
<p local-id=3D"ad0c0ebbdaac">Verify health checks and logs.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"9560ba9a-5eff-446a-8dc8-236f8b0980b9">
<p local-id=3D"900d0849e46b">Monitor AWS billing dashboard.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"d02c462b-bc0a-4071-9282-e7f28a0e78a1">
<h1 local-id=3D"271169cd836f" id=3D"T4-RequirementAnalysisDocument-7.Glossa=
ry">7. Glossary</h1>
<ul local-id=3D"f583563e-49da-4064-bac4-5603e0c658fa">
<li local-id=3D"1bf73551-5568-475c-90d2-937b68587443">
<p local-id=3D"91dc32ee2da3">Static Hosting =E2=80=93 Serving static files =
without backend processing.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"eb483243-907f-447a-b3c1-875363df2102">
<p local-id=3D"0fbf22bc8c6e">Container =E2=80=93 Lightweight packaged appli=
cation runtime.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bbfda3bb-11b8-4162-8243-78239885ba48">
<p local-id=3D"931dee5f4ecc">Load Balancer =E2=80=93 Distributes incoming t=
raffic.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1b1ae97a-d9d9-4246-84b3-3b0a8b31dfb7">
<p local-id=3D"4c5bafe04dd2">Public IP =E2=80=93 Internet-accessible addres=
s of EC2 instance.</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"2a821530-48a1-4342-bf6d-935cdc0d87d7">
<h1 local-id=3D"367de09832ce" id=3D"T4-RequirementAnalysisDocument-8.Append=
ices">8. Appendices</h1>
<ul local-id=3D"e22bce29-fe37-4b7e-b3ed-eb818f7e1c68">
<li local-id=3D"3d53e485-c3ac-40c1-ae5c-cd44f8c846e6">
<p local-id=3D"526e5506ff5f">Deployment screenshots</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5f73c6d8-333b-4b68-a87c-b015b4d43a29">
<p local-id=3D"1df001348c3d">ECS architecture diagram</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8bae5b4e-aca9-45b2-9b2a-970c0b5db8ca">
<p local-id=3D"f81335e3abbc">S3 static hosting configuration</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"06a9857d-eba9-4c1c-84b5-3f33a662b8dc">
<p local-id=3D"f492d95361f9">EC2 Nginx configuration commands</p></li>
</ul>
